 Nehal Aftab — Portfolio

Personal portfolio website built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Serves as a living resume showcasing my projects, skills, and experience.

Live Site: Nehal Aftab — Portfolio

Personal portfolio website built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Serves as a living resume showcasing my projects, skills, and experience.

🔗 Live Site:  (https://github.com/naynay575)


 Tech Stack

HTML5 · CSS3 · Vanilla JavaScript · Google Fonts (DM Serif Display, Inter, JetBrains Mono)

Features

- Fully responsive — works on mobile, tablet, and desktop
- Smooth scroll-reveal animations on every section
- Animated hero with ambient gradient orb
- Sticky nav with scroll-triggered background blur
- Dark theme with periwinkle/violet accent palette
- Sections: Hero · About · Skills · Projects · Experience · Contact

